<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf3d9ca8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11294"><num value="11294">§ 11294.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idbf3d9ca9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11294/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> To carry out sections 11291 and 11293 of this title, there are authorized to be appropriated $1,000,000 for each of the fiscal years 1988 through 1991.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idbf3d9caa-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11294/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content> There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1992 through 1996, to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s11292">section 11292 of this title</ref>.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idbf3d9cab-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/660/tIX/s964">Pub. L. 99–660, title IX, § 964</ref>, <date date="1986-11-14">Nov. 14, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3815">100 Stat. 3815</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/507/s8/b">Pub. L. 102–507, § 8(b)</ref>, <date date="1992-10-24">Oct. 24, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/3287">106 Stat. 3287</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbf3d9cac-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbf3d9cad-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbf3d9cae-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1992—<ref href="/us/pl/102/507">Pub. L. 102–507</ref> designated existing provisions as subsec. (a), substituted “sections 11291 and 11293 of this title” for “this subchapter”, and added subsec. (b).</p>
</note>
</notes>
